title: Brillar Uprising
description: Conquest cannot be stopped... The future. An Iberian mining outpost on the planet Brillar is troubled by the uprising of the natives. The government in Madrid sends a legendary conquistador to put an end to the armed insurgency. Spilling Brillarian blood, he discovers that it's not the indigenous inhabitants of the planet who pose the threat.
